<p><span style="font-size: 16px;">[4] Chen, R., Xu, X., &amp; Shen, H. (2017). Go beyond just paying: Effects of payment method on level of construal. Journal of Consumer Psychology, 27(2), 207–217.</span></p>
<p><span style="font-size: 16px;">[5] 张美萱, 吴瑞林, 张涵, 田奕真, 杨鹿野, 姚唐. (2018). “电子钱包”让人花钱更多？——手机支付的心理账户效应. 心理科学, 41(4), 904–909.</span></p>
<p><span style="font-size: 16px;">[6] Prelec, D., &amp; Loewenstein, G. (1998). The Red and the Black: Mental Accounting of Savings and Debt. Marketing Science, 17(1), 4–28. </span></p>
